{"tid":1662464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10月21會出席嘅人入！邊個話要忘記721單野？？","createTime":"2019-10-18T18:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T18:15:47.000Z","uid":219635,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e49129e19f748a2757b78bc8021a73224fd2fa","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"單野過左成3個月，社會已經慢慢比人帶風向去左其他事件。但721呢件警黑勾結最明顯嘅事件，竟然開始冇乜人關心，唔通你地已經忘記咗？？<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有不少人係到講：元朗班鄉黑搞左咁大單野一定驚收唔到科，唔會再出嚟搞事架啦，同埋黑警都知玩大左，唔會再發生同樣事情架啦⋯⋯之類嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 全世界去哂查案呀，裝修呀，我都明白發生太多事，大家都顧唔到邊樣，顧緊呢樣又冇啦啦有第二樣野搶哂fol。<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚,元朗西鐵站樓下連儂牆又上演左一場警黑勾結，<br />\n接近幾十人嘅鄉黑/白衣又出現元朗西鐵站樓下去做撕紙狗，當然附近有好多文宣手足，雙方都起哄，最後由防暴掩護下，鄉黑成功撕哂文宣仲走佬。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔明點解仲有人覺得唔嚴重，仲覺得元朗都唔係好藍姐，覺得班鄉下佬垃圾721之後有撚膽再出現咩，之類。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚元朗鄉黑就話比全香港知：我721可以搞到你地班廢青驚，代表我隨時都可以搞鑊比你地班人。唔撚好再係我地頭搞事，元朗係黑社會話事，要搞民主爭取自由，問過我地班鄉親父老未？你幾勇武都唔撚夠黑社會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以往各區都會有發生零星撕紙狗同手足衝突事件，但都係得幾個人做撕紙狗/休班狗，有個別撕紙狗都可以比人鶳到，但元朗就一出就成班幾十個鄉黑出嚟，唔好話鶳，你唔比佢地鶳已經很好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我講咁多，都係知道就嚟又係10月21即是發生第三個月，等大家唔好忘記，唔好忘記勇武嘅重要性，1020你可以和理非阻人勇武，<br />\n但1021，自己醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你搞元朗連儂搞左成3個月，元朗西鐵站附近就係幾條村，佢地今晚出嚟試水溫已經代表班鄉黑忍你地好撚耐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZve32r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZve32r.jpg&h=ef68707f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZ4vCnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZ4vCnu.jpg&h=a1aabde1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da4c5c15cc512993ac828e61e393b8d6f29d2eb3","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804bfc30ab1a81e443b516189f79a15617e47fa3","tid":1662464,"uid":26952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"10.20見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcRaCh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcRaCh8.png&h=6a019475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a9f52e937a20a190248eba4615cb5a1812139c7","tid":1662464,"uid":288830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/enANcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/enANcS</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推！"},{"pid":"9f591a5fec6cb5f6451f0e3a9861117f173a36bb","tid":1662464,"uid":283686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇可能忘記"},{"pid":"3fb1698343b80e4f7326fb22193d361ed9bf41d9","tid":1662464,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:05:49.000Z","msg":"Truly Not UNTIL popo have found all  those WHITE - shirt men, it should not be forgotten in future history of HK.<br />\n<br />\n21th of each month -  is a memorial day  passing from generations to generations !!<br />\n<br />\nLam and popo should have the responsibilities to find out those who commited the crime! We are talking about  HUNDREDS.<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><br />\nDig out  the name of popo who is in charge of this case. <br />\nI wonder how many men hours have popo put into this case.</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f49833ae8b69108734f2b2a171d9b3050dbc940a","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"大家睇下，鄉黑閒閒地吹雞清連儂牆已經有幾十人，當中班你地口中嘅廢中/老都係手持武器，街坊同市民都驚到只識拍片。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yMaRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yMaRo.png&h=79c96d64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWQZvRB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWQZvRB.png&h=382f47a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5B1NEK8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5B1NEK8.png&h=a349e38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真心諗下，如果721重演，手足應唔應付到？唔好同福建佬比較，鄉黑絕對唔同北角福建佬級數。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"173bb810eae34e0070171f2ed64601cdca4d1732","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3db32796b1857cd185a0c1a5dab8734a962a02","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5dd56ccac77bfd6586c2b068823d16cba5fc6c","tid":1662464,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"絕不忘記721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ffbfab97d05ab377d694d1b777da5a082864e2","tid":1662464,"uid":28009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:10:09.000Z","msg":"推 唔會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf0cfafea6e4f2ba6d4f0c928a74670b6e81b3a","tid":1662464,"uid":28009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86cc5bf1957ee96207606b37530625d6fb019ad5","tid":1662464,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:11:37.000Z","msg":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e501872015c6736c80854b83ac12d31a022b3b14","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de3f2051b3e87491feb21719c34de96c3190106","tid":1662464,"uid":166258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:16:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07e4963e5f8befc57dce345125872c86ebdcc1a8","tid":1662464,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NE7AO3i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNE7AO3i.png&h=c27d3e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6edb08433bd7c721cdc718cd15b8e9c3a80f2d18","tid":1662464,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:46:15.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"b134fe12b9378d70b3f2c7015075ffba2495a6e0","tid":1662464,"uid":83072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:17:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0bbbb0b87cd7eedfae35dd084608de57b2c7d8c0","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeff2d6670e916cbb168fe0a08000550fa145243","tid":1662464,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273d1e255479d66a151c4f859d5fa65ff0a080d1","tid":1662464,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"政府死穴-7.21三個月6區地鐵站靜坐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6334d8e7ae6ca451d3c1d222745a33e68a01eca","tid":1662464,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}